data.description: Price Improvement!  MAGNIFICENT HOME IN A GREAT NEIGHBORHOOD OF STONEY CREEK. Upon entry, you are greeted with a spacious two-story foyer, Dining Room, and an Office.  Primary is on main floor with a charming en suite featuring a spa-like bathtub, and separate shower.  Great room with a cozy fireplace.  Landscaped backyard with gorgeous deck space great for entertaining!  Upstairs features two additional bedrooms, and bath.
